        <briefdescription>
<para>Converts timestamps from MLTime to system time. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>See <ref refid="group___common_1ga39ed24b20d4477f2d684e554df0e582f" kindref="member">MLTime</ref> for more details. System time is equivalent to the systems monotonic clock. This can be used to calculate duration between two MLTime values by converting them both to a timespec and subtracting the subsequent values.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>API Level:\n 20</title><para></para>
</simplesect>
