</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">out_timespec_time</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to a converted equivalent timestamp as if received from clock_gettime using CLOCK_MONOTONIC.</para>
